snippet.title: Turok: Escape from Lost Valley Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Do you remember Turok the Dinosaur Hunter? This is not that Turok. This is Turok, but cute. Take a look at the isometric action in this gameplay trailer for Turok: Escape from Lost Valley, a new game from Pillow Pig Games and Universal Studios Interactive Entertainment.

Turok: Escape from Lost Valley releases on Steam on July 25.
